<div class="en">
Together with your children<br>
find sound-making objects in the home<br>
Use existing instruments<br>
Raid the kitchen cupboard<br>
or make your own.

Discover<br>
loud and soft sounds<br>
long and short sounds<br>
high and low pitches<br>
bright and dark colours<br>
Spend time to explore them<br>
and make them close their eyes<br>
to listen to the resonance.

Make your own musical score together<br>
(there are no fixed rules)<br>
Use many colours to represent<br>
the different elements<br>
Let your child lead the process<br>
Then perform it together.
</div>